>Burner/Element Output N4</strong>: 2500 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N5</strong>: 3200 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N6</strong>: 1800 Watts</li><br><p><strong>Oven</strong></p><li><strong>Oven Control Type</strong>: TFT Electronic Touchscreen</li><li><strong>Oven Door Type</strong>: Solid Door</li><li><strong>Oven Cleaning Type</strong>: Easy Clean Enamel Cavities</li><li><strong>Main Oven Type</strong>: UOV 60 E3 TFT S</li><li><strong>Interior Width</strong>: 18 1/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Interior Height</strong>: 14 1/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Interior Depth</strong>: 16 1/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Second Oven Type</strong>: UOV 30 E3 TFT</li><li><strong>Secondary Interior Width</strong>: 10 7/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Secondary Interior Height</strong>: 14\\u2033</li><li><strong>Secondary Interior Depth</strong>: 17 1/3\\u2033</li><br><p><strong>Technical Details</strong></p><li><strong>Voltage</strong>: 240</li><li><strong>Amps</strong>: 75.6</li><br/><p><strong>Certifications</strong></p><li><strong>Star-K Certified</strong>: Yes</li><br/><p><strong>Warranty</strong></p><li><strong>Warranty</strong>: 2 Year Parts and Labor</li><br/><p><strong>Features</strong></p><li><strong>Sabbath Mode</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Display Type</strong>: TFT Display</li><li><strong>Number of Racks</strong>: 2 Rack</li><li><strong>Drawer</strong>: Warming Drawer</li><li><strong>Timer</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Temperature Probe</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Rotisserie</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Soft Close Door</strong>: Yes</li></br></br></br></br></ul> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_shipping-returns\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"shipping-returns\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_shipping-returns\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Shipping/Returns</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"