rong>Sabbath Mode</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Display Type</strong>: TFT Display</li><li><strong>Number of Racks</strong>: 2 Rack</li><li><strong>Drawer</strong>: Warming Drawer</li><li><strong>Timer</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Temperature Probe</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Rotisserie</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Soft Close Door</strong>: Yes</li></br></br></br></br></ul> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_shipping-returns\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"shipping-returns\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_shipping-returns\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Shipping/Returns</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_shipping-returns\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_shipping-returns\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">            Please review Castle &amp; Cabana's <strong>Return, Refund, Exchange</strong> and <strong>Shipping Policies</strong> carefully, as certain brands may have specific terms that differ from our general store policies.            <br/><br/>            For detailed information, please refer to the following sections:            <br/>            1. <strong><a href=\\\"/pages/refund-and-return-policy\\\">Refund and Return Policy</a></strong> <br/>            2. <strong><a href=\\\"/pages/shipping-policy\\\">Shipping Policy</a></strong> <br/><br/>            If you have any questions or require further clarification, our team is happy to assist you. Kindly contact us at: <strong><a href=\\\"mailto:sales@castleandcabana.com\\\">sales@castleandcabana.com</a></strong> <br/><br/> <strong>Note</strong>: Some items are available for pre-order with an estimated delivery time of 90-120 days, including custom-made products such as select sauna cabins, luxury appliances, and other special-order